<td colspan=2 bgcolor="#0000AF"><font color=white>Casters are so easy to get over 200 int its not funny. <BR>
At 200 int you want to start adding mana items since everything<BR>
over 200 only adds one point of mana. So 55 mana is like 5.5<BR>
int, you get 10 mana for every point up to 200. So that why<BR>
you start to see casters looking for Mana things. This necklace<BR>
is also used for making the White Dragon Scale Cloak (9 wis 9 int<BR>
75 mana 25 resist cold). I have seen many things trade for these<BR>
items ykesha's, efreeti boots, SMR's etc. Thing is even a maxed<BR>
out jewel maker with Bard or enchanter or both still fails alot <BR>
on this. Black saphires are very rare also. The success is higher<BR>
on the earrings.</font></td></tr></table>
