<td width=50%><font color=white>Posted By: Matron Lolthe A`rachnith</font></td><td width=50% align=right><font color=white>2000-03-02 11:51:32</font></td></tr><tr>
<td colspan=2 bgcolor="#0000AF"><font color=white>The Blackened Sapphire (aka Sapphire of Souls) is dropped by a level 22-24 placeholding Rogue NPC named Ekeron in the outerchamber of Rathyl, in the dungeon of Najena.  He spawns at a rate of 1 in 3 in place of one of the Magicians, and carries the stone 4 out of 5 times. This stone looks like an ice cream cone when wielded, and sells for 100pp on E`ci server. As for the Patinum bar, 105pp is my cost, but even at max jewelry skill, high plat often fails..............</font></td></tr></table>
