<td colspan=2 bgcolor="#0000AF"><font color=white>Ok school is in again so listen up newbs. IT is not the blacken[ED] Sapphire. It is the stone that is stackable that drops in all planes and on any lvl 50 mobs anywhere. I assure you that you have never bought one for 30 plat. So until you get a clue listen to what i say. Casters are simple to get over 200 int add the necklace and 2 earrings and you have 125 extra mana, i have over 350 extra item with all my mana items and still have over 200 int.</font></td></tr></table>
